						<div class="postbody">Are you resetting the name table index ($2000) and the scroll ($2005) after using $2006 and $2007? If not, this is most likely what's killing your background. Using $2006 and $2007 fucks up the scroll, so after you're finished with them you have to reposition the scroll using $2000 and $2005, like you probably did when setting up the background the first time.</div>

