					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Reading or writing from 2007 increments the PPU address by 1.  Need to read the byte, then write the address again if you want to rewrite the byte.
<br />
<br />Also, scrolling and the PPU address use the same internal registers on the PPU, so every time you change stuff on the screen, you need to reset the scrolling.  Scrolling first then writing new ppu data won't do any good.  Need to scroll last.</div>

					
